  "locationDetails": [
    {
      "title": "Neighborhood highlights",
      "html": "This cabin is about 20 minutes from downtown Mariposa, which is full of cute shops and cafes. Grab a coffee at Moonbow, a bite to eat at 1850 Brewery, and a beer at The Alley (or Hideout if you're feeling adventurous). High Country Health Foods has vegetarian and vegan options and Pioneer Market can be your one-stop-shop for groceries and beverages. Our place is also about 20 minutes fro Oakhurst, where there's more restaurants and grocery stores. Depending on which way you come in, there's a grocery store on your way."
    }
  ],
